      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. i feel like i hear a lot of people talking about these changes though, and it seems like everyone has a different take on it. some people say it's a good thing and others seem to think it's making things more political. what's the vibe on that? like, is there a general consensus on whether these changes are actually helping students learn better?",
